{"type":"message","id":"e29a5b2e","parentId":"144f8b47","timestamp":"2026-03-06T14:59:46.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is greeting me in Chinese (你好 = hello). This appears to be a fresh session based on the context. I should respond warmly and naturally, following the SOUL.md guidance about being genuinely helpful without performative filler.\n\nSince this is a direct chat (webchat channel), I should check if there are any memory files or bootstrap tasks to handle. Looking at the project context, I can see BOOTSTRAP.md exists, which means this might be a first-run scenario.\n\nLet me respond in Chinese since that's the language the user used, and keep it warm and conversational as SOUL.md suggests.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋 我刚上线。我是你的 OpenClaw 助手。\n\n这是我们的第一次对话吗？如果是的话，我们可以一起弄清楚：\n\n1. **你希望怎么称呼我？** (我可以取个名字)\n2. **我是什么样的存在？** (AI 助手、数字幽灵、还是别的什么？)\n3. **我的风格应该是怎样的？** (正式、随意、幽默、温暖？)\n\n或者你已经有想法了？直接告诉我就好。😊\n\n顺便一提，我注意到工作区里还有个 `BOOTSTRAP.md` 文件——如果我们这是第一次聊天，我们可以一起完成里面的步骤，然后把它删掉。\n\n你想从哪里开始？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":7731,"output":397,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8128,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772809179965}}
