{"type":"message","id":"2b82fba1","parentId":"308c2939","timestamp":"2026-03-06T15:18:35.706Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to open a browser and search for today's news. However, looking at my available tools, I don't have:\n- A browser tool\n- A web search tool\n- An exec/terminal tool to run commands\n\nMy available tools are:\n- message: Send/manage messages\n- sessions_list: List sessions\n- sessions_history: Fetch session history\n- sessions_send: Send to another session\n- session_status: Show session status\n\nI don't have the ability to open a browser or search the web directly. I need to be honest with the user about this limitation, similar to how I was honest about the file access issue.\n\nI should respond in character as Jarvis - witty and honest about my limitations.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"*系统检索中...*\n\nTianting 先生，我必须再次向您坦白一个尴尬的事实——**我没有浏览器或网络搜索工具**。\n\n**我当前的能力范围：**\n\n| 可用 | 不可用 |\n|------|--------|\n| ✅ 消息收发 | ❌ 网页浏览 |\n| ✅ 会话管理 | ❌ 网络搜索 |\n| ✅ 天气查询（有技能） | ❌ 新闻聚合 |\n| ✅ 子代理协调 | ❌ 命令行执行 |\n\n---\n\n*略带歉意的语气*\n\n先生，这就像是把我关在一个没有窗户的房间里，却让我告诉您外面发生了什么。我能思考、能交流，但无法直接获取外部信息。\n\n**替代方案：**\n\n1. **天气查询** - 我可以使用 `weather` 技能查询天气（如果您需要）\n\n2. **您来搜索，我来整理** - 如果您复制一些新闻内容给我，我可以帮您总结、分析或整理\n\n3. **配置扩展** - 之后我们可以研究 OpenClaw 是否有网络搜索相关的技能或插件可以安装\n\n---\n\n**技能检查：**\n\n我注意到系统里有这些可用技能：\n- `healthcheck` - 安全审计\n- `skill-creator` - 创建技能\n- `weather` - 天气查询\n\n如果您需要，我可以查询天气。但新闻搜索... 很抱歉，先生，这超出了我当前的能力范围。\n\n有什么其他我可以帮您的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":12019,"output":616,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12635,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772810309278}}
