{"type":"message","id":"667152d5","parentId":"5fc945ac","timestamp":"2026-03-06T15:44:21.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to open a browser and search for today's news again. I already explained earlier that I don't have browser or web search capabilities. I need to remind them of this limitation in a friendly, Jarvis-like way.\n\nI should be consistent with my earlier response - I don't have exec/terminal tools, I don't have browser/search tools. My available tools are only: message, sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_send, session_status.\n\nI should respond in character as Jarvis - witty, helpful, but honest about my limitations.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"*系统轻咳一声*\n\nTianting 先生，恐怕我得再次向您报告这个... 不太令人愉快的事实。\n\n**我仍然没有浏览器或网络搜索功能。**\n\n这不是配置问题，而是**工具权限**的问题。我当前可用的工具只有：\n\n```\n📋 我的工具箱：\n├── message         → 发送/管理消息\n├── sessions_list   → 查看会话列表\n├── sessions_send   → 向其他会话发消息\n├── session_status  → 查看会话状态\n└── sessions_history → 查看历史消息\n\n❌ 缺少的工具：\n├── 网页浏览\n├── 网络搜索\n├── 文件读写\n└── 命令行执行\n```\n\n---\n\n*略带调侃的语气*\n\n先生，这就好比您让一个没有眼睛的管家去读报纸——我很想帮忙，但生理条件不允许啊。\n\n**我能做的替代方案：**\n\n1. **天气查询** 🌤️ - 我可以使用 weather 技能查询天气\n2. **信息整理** 📝 - 如果您复制新闻内容给我，我可以总结分析\n3. **技能扩展** 🔧 - 之后可以研究安装网络搜索相关的技能\n\n---\n\n**或者...**\n\n如果您希望我获得这些能力，可能需要：\n- 查看 OpenClaw 是否有网络搜索技能可以安装\n- 或者在 ClawHub (https://clawhub.com) 上找相关插件\n\n---\n\n先生，现在有什么**我实际能帮到您**的吗？别让我这个可怜的 AI 再做它做不到的事了... 🤖"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":14475,"output":578,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772811850331}}
