{"type":"message","id":"d4ceb810","parentId":"78d44364","timestamp":"2026-03-06T15:48:09.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to open a browser and search for today's news again - this is the third time they've asked this. I've already explained twice that I don't have browser or web search capabilities.\n\nI need to be honest but also not keep repeating the same explanation in exactly the same way. Let me be direct and clear, but also offer a practical alternative or ask if there's something else I can actually help with.\n\nI should not pretend I can do something I cannot do. I need to be clear about my limitations while remaining helpful in tone.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"*系统轻声叹息*\n\nTianting 先生，我必须再次诚实告知您：\n\n**我无法打开浏览器，也无法搜索新闻。**\n\n这不是配置问题，也不是权限问题——是我**根本没有这个工具**。\n\n---\n\n**我能做的：**\n- ✅ 查询天气\n- ✅ 发送/管理消息\n- ✅ 会话管理\n- ✅ 整理您提供的信息\n\n**我做不到的：**\n- ❌ 网页浏览\n- ❌ 网络搜索\n- ❌ 文件读写\n- ❌ 执行命令\n\n---\n\n*诚恳的语气*\n\n先生，我知道这可能让人沮丧。您想要一个能干的贾维斯，但我目前的能力有限。\n\n**如果您需要今日新闻，建议：**\n1. 您自行浏览新闻网站\n2. 复制内容给我，我帮您总结整理\n3. 或者研究 OpenClaw 是否有新闻/搜索技能可以安装\n\n---\n\n现在，有什么**我实际能帮您**的事情吗？🤖"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":14899,"output":441,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15340,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772812082681}}
